{"title":"Ubuntu安装jenkins","date":"2020-09-22T08:16:29.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Sep 22, 2020","L":"09/22/2020","MM-DD":"09-22"},"link":"2020/09/22/ubuntu-install-jenkins","tags":["jenkins"],"categories":["jenkins"],"updated":"2020-09-22T09:42:53.474Z","content":"<p><strong>在进行此操作前，首先需要满足以下条件：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>一个Ubuntu 16.04 或者 Ubuntu18.04服务器<br>\n配置了非root用户和防火墙，遵循Ubuntu 16.04初始服务器设置指南 。 我们建议从至少1 GB的RAM开始。 请参阅为大师准备正确的硬件，以指导生产Jenkins安装的容量。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"安装java-sdk\">安装Java SDK<a title=\"#安装java-sdk\" href=\"#安装java-sdk\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#sudo apt-get install openjdk-7-jdk  早些系统可以安装</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo apt-get install openjdk-8-jdk</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"安装jenkins\">安装Jenkins<a title=\"#安装jenkins\" href=\"#安装jenkins\"></a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"相关链接\">相关链接<a title=\"#相关链接\" href=\"#相关链接\"></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/845f267aec52\" title=\"如何在Ubuntu 16.04上安装Jenkins\" target=\"_blank\">如何在Ubuntu 16.04上安装Jenkins</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"linux下更新jenkins","link":"2020/09/22/linux-update-jenkins"},"next":{"title":"docker安装consul","link":"2020/09/10/docker-install-consul"},"plink":"http://blog.arytry.com/2020/09/22/ubuntu-install-jenkins/","toc":[{"id":"安装java-sdk","title":"安装Java SDK","index":"1"},{"id":"安装jenkins","title":"安装Jenkins","index":"2"},{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","index":"3"}],"reward":true}